metadata.name: Space Travel
metadata.description:
"As I ride the ferry, the vessel suddenly shifts and I find myself in space, confronted by the vast expanse of the universe. The beauty and complexity of creation leave me humbled yet filled with a sense of wonder and excitement for the mysteries that await us in the cosmos."

*Digital Painting + Mixed Media | After Kristopher Shinn | 2023*

**"Space Travel" is an exclusive BWOW inspired airdrop, created by Postwook, for holders of "By Way of Water"**
